Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:28.22,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}It's been so long since we left our home behind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:34.48,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Drifting on the Milky Way almost every single day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.94,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where am I supposed to go ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:41.02,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}What're we really looking for ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:46.11,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Stumbling in the darkness, cold and lost
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:52.99,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}But a ray of hope still exists in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:58.50,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Rain or shine, always chase the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:02.63,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Someday, we'll fly across the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:06.09,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never fearing anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:10.89,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We'll promise that"we'll go on ! "
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:15.06,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if you're against the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:16.56,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never stop !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:18.31,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Don't look back !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:23.73,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We'll one day rise above it all (never give up)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:27.57,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Who cares if the going's tough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.65,0:22:29.11,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never think !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:30.99,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Keep pushing on !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:38.08,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We can find our promised land
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:28.22,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}离乡远行 已经历漫长时光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:34.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}年年日日 漂泊在星河八荒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.94,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我欲去往何处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:41.02,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我在追寻何物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:46.11,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}寒冷 迷茫 在黑暗中流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:52.99,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但我心中仍存一线希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:58.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}无论风雨 始终追寻梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:02.63,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}总有一天 我们将横越苍茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:06.09,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}无所畏惧 展翼翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:10.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我们许下誓言 绝不退让
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:15.06,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即便逆流而上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:16.56,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不要停下脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:18.31,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}切莫顾盼彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:23.73,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}终有一日 我们将迎来风雨后的辉煌（绝不退让）
